"Yes, you were fighting with a burglar when he ransacked your girlfriends apartment, you fought with the assailant and he fled, you then chased him to the roof, when he drew a knife and cut you, in defence you tackled the criminal and in the struggle you both fall, landing on top of him breaking your fall, he then slipped away into the morning sun"
